duties_responsibilities.duty: Loading, unloading, and sorting packages of various sizes in a fast-paced warehouse environment.
Working one shift a day for part-time employees, and two shifts for full-time employees.
Balancing work and personal life with flexible scheduling.
Part-time employees working between 3 and 6 hours a day, and full-time employees working between 6 and 10 hours.
Receiving overtime pay after 40 hours a week.
